# Frontend Rules

## Mobile-First
- Start at 320px, scale up
- Use responsive Tailwind: `text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl`
- Minimum touch targets: 44x44px
- Test: 320px → 375px → 768px → 1024px → 1440px

## Copywriting
- Simple, authentic, human
- No: "revolutionary", "game-changing", "cutting-edge"
- Yes: direct, factual, transparent

## Stack
- Next.js App Router
- Tailwind CSS
- TypeScript strict

## Performance
- Lazy load below-fold content
- Optimize images (next/image)
- Minimal JS bundle
- Server components by default
